hts. We take Tennis as an example, established a GBP-radar judgment AI model, which combined with radar chart and GBP score model which is accumulated with base score, hold score, break score and score in a raw. The higher the GBP score, the better the performance. And the GBP score results of both players are calculated on a per set basis. Bringing the data of the 2023-wimbledon-1701 match, we found out that Carlos Alcaraz had a higher GBP score in the second set, the third set and the fifth set, and performed better, which is closely matched with the actual win/loss results, as well as plotted a radar chart to analyze the degree of good performance of the players who performed well.},
